[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "（システム）",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "遡ること数日――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_720_037_00038",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 965274698
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（順調なら、あと何日かしたら\n　みんなは雷鳴の島か……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00039",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（やっぱりアタシもついていけたら、\n　よかったんだけどなぁ……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00040",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（なんか旅をしてたら、自信がつくような\n　必殺技を編み出せるか、なんて思ってたけど）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00041",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "上手くはいかんかったーーーい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00042",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（いざってときに怖くて動けない足手まといなんて\n　なんの役にも立たないよね）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00043",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "はぁ……情けないアルビちゃん……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00044",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（みんなと別れてから、アタシは錬金術を忘れて\n　いつもの案内人として生活してみた）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00045",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（怖いことなんてなんもない。安定してて、\n　みんな優しくて、安全な一日）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00046",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（多分、望むんならこんな穏やかな毎日が\n　ずっと続いていくんだろう。死ぬまで……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00047",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そんな退屈な一生……考えただけで震えるわ……\nアタシは、そんなの嫌だ。で、でも……でもぉ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00048",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "姉様……寝てた？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00049",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ううん。ちょっとわがままな考えごとしてただけ。\nごめんね、情けない姉様で",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00050",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "私は、姉様が自分のこと、どう思ってたっていい。\n私にとって姉様が英雄であることに変わりはないから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00051",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "……ああ、もしかして水不足の時の話？\nあれはただ、師匠のお膳立てがあったからで……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00052",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "ううん。\nそれもあるけど、もっと個人的な話",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00053",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "私の生まれた島は、赤く光る魔物に滅ぼされた。\nお母さんも、お父さんも、友達も、みんな死んだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00054",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "その時から私の心にあったのはヤツに対する復讐心、\nただそれだけだった……私は空っぽだった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00055",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ベップ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00056",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "でも姉様は、そんな私の手を引いて案内してくれた。\n楽しい場所、同い年の子がいる場所、色んな遊び――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00057",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "白黒だった世界に、少しずつ色が戻り始めた……\n姉様の宝石みたいな目の色、綺麗だなって思った",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00058",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "私は姉様のおかげで、前を向けるようになったわ。\n復讐だけじゃないって、生きる気力が湧いてきたの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00059",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん……確かに出会ったばかりのベップは、\nどこか心ここにあらずなところがあったというか……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00060",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "ん……熊の魔物に挑んだ時のこと、覚えてる？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00061",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "……あー、はいはい！　アタシがたまたま\n洗濯サボって遊んでたら川上にベップと熊がいてね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00062",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "当時の私に、あの魔物は荷が重かった。\n危なかったところを、姉様が救ってくれた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00063",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "救ったっていうか、洗濯石鹸を投げて\n魔物を滑って転ばせただけだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00064",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "おかげで私は逃げられた。姉様がいなかったら\n私も今、ここにはいないから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00065",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "それにその後、とっておきの場所に\n案内してくれた、よね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00066",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん。森を抜けた先にある崖地の端っこ。\n海が見えて、人も船もあまり通らなくて――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00067",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "遠くまで空と海が見渡せる、姉様だけの場所",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00068",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そ、だからとっておき。誰にも聞かれないから、\n気晴らしにあそこで歌うの、好きだったんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00069",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "あの時も姉様は言ってくれたわ。\nここなら誰にも見られない、泣いていいんだよって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00070",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "姉様のおかげで……私はあれから初めて、\nちゃんと泣くことができた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00071",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "だから、あの日から……誰も、姉様本人が\n認めていなくても、姉様は私にとって英雄……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00072",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ん……ありがと。\nなんか、こっちが救われた、かも",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00073",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（たとえ何があっても、自分の味方でいてくれる。\n　そんな人がいるなんて、アタシ、幸せ者だな）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00074",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（それに「案内」か。アタシはなんだかんだで\n　案内するのが得意で、アタシらしさなんだろうな）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00075",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "あ……私、姉様を呼びに来たんだった。\nヤンネさんに頼まれて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00076",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ん？　なんだろ？　ベップは心当たりある？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00077",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "いいえ、ないわ。カフェで待ってるって言ってたから\nとりあえず行ってみましょ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00078",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]